wiki.content: “Young & Alive” is a single track that was announced on Bazzi’s socials two days before its release. He posted a teaser for the music video on his Instagram a day later. The track is highly reminiscent of his personal upbringing, recalling simpler times and how his partner enables him to return to this sense of youth and freedom. "for me – i’ve felt like a certain feeling in music has been missing. i wanted to make something that reminded me of the beauty and mystery of being young – sumn that would take me back to that place of naive freedom" –Bazzi via Twitter (March 4th, 2020) Read more on Last.fm.
